    public class Obstacle
extends Grid

    Obstacle

    A Obstacle is a Grid located in a Map. No MovableGrid is allowed to move across it.

    This class extends Grid.

    1.0

    • Constructor Detail

      • Obstacle

        public Obstacle​(Map map,
                double row,
                double column)
        Allocates a new Obstacle object.

        This constructor sets the Obstacle in the given position of the given Map, AND sets an image of wall.

        Parameters:
        map - the Map where this Cookie stays
        row - the row index in the Map where this Obstacle stays, starting from 0
        column - the column index in the Map where this Obstacle stays, starting from 0
